---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Walk-In Urgent Care in Dallas–Fort Worth — No Appointment Needed | AymanCare"
  description="Same-day walk-in urgent care for illness and minor injuries at four Dallas-area clinics. No appointment needed — just show up during business hours."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Walk-In Urgent Care\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/walk-in-urgent-care/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Walk-In Urgent Care</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Same-day · No appointment</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><em>Walk-in</em><br>urgent care.</h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">Same-day care for the unexpected. Minor injuries, acute illness, rapid testing — when you need a clinician now, not next week.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">No appointment</span><span class="pill pill-accent">All ages</span><span class="pill">COVID testing on-site</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book this visit →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/clinic-exterior.jpeg" alt="Walk-In Urgent Care">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Service details</div>
        <h3>We <em>treat</em></h3>
        <ul><li>Colds, flu, strep throat</li><li>Minor injuries & sprains</li><li>Cuts, burns, rashes</li><li>UTIs & infections</li><li>COVID-19 testing & treatment</li><li>Ear, nose, throat issues</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Ready to book?</div>
        <h3>Same-day <em>appointments</em> available.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Call or book online — walk-ins welcome at every location.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2>Walk-in care, when life <em>won't wait.</em></h2><p>Life rarely sticks to a schedule. That's why AymanCare is set up to handle the unexpected — walk in for a sore throat, an ankle you rolled on the stairs, or the moment you realize you really do need to see someone today.</p><h2>Faster than the <em>ER.</em></h2><p>Most urgent care visits cost a fraction of an emergency room visit and are dramatically faster. For non-life-threatening conditions, AymanCare walk-in is the right first stop — board-certified care, standard clinic pricing, and a team who will refer you up if you need it.</p><blockquote>"Walk-in care should feel like running into your doctor — not navigating a hospital."</blockquote><h2><em>COVID-19</em> testing & treatment.</h2><p>We offer rapid and PCR COVID-19 testing on-site at all four locations. If you test positive, we can provide same-visit treatment guidance, prescribe antivirals where appropriate, and help you plan the next few days with your family in mind.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col"><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">< 30min</div>
      <h4>Average wait</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">7 days</div>
      <h4>Walk-ins welcome</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Rapid</div>
      <h4>COVID & flu tests</h4>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<section class="related-services">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
        <div>
          <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid"><a href="/services/primary-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Primary</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Long-term care and annual wellness — your family physician.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/pediatric-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Pediatric</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Child-centered care from newborn to teen.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/flu-treatment/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Flu</em> Symptoms</h4>
          <p>Rapid flu diagnosis and treatment.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a></div>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Ready when you are</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's take care<br>of <em>you.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Book online in under a minute, or walk into any of our four Dallas-area locations today.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
